
'''= carpooling initiative and app based in Ghent, Belgium'''

URL: https://www.fstr.eu/en/

=Description=

FSTR has developed an app which brings travellers in contact with drivers headed in the same direction. These people are brought together via the app and can then arrange for a carpool. Both drivers and passengers can use the app. This saves money, time and the environment. 

===== FSTR Mobility =====
FSTR MOBILITY provides a handy app to combine all data from private cars, train, trams and busses.

===== FSTR Data=====
FSTR DATA provides open source data from private cars, train, trams and buses to professional app developers.


